      <title>星巴克裁员背后：英国与香港办公室缩编，连锁咖啡重组进入“效率优先”新阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/xing-ba-ke-cai-yuan-bei-hou-ying-guo-yu-xiang-gang/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 19:46:43 +0800</pubDate>
